# Tool Matrix — Required Tools per Phase

## Cardinal Rule
"Se a ferramenta existe e e relevante, o sistema FORCA seu uso."

## Research Phase
| Tool | Required | When |
|------|----------|------|
| firecrawl_agent | YES | Autonomous data collection |
| voc_search | YES | Validate hypotheses |
| fb_ad_library.get_meta_ads | YES | Discover competitors |
| fb_ad_library.analyze_ad_video | YES | TOP 5 video analysis |
| playwright | FALLBACK | Sites blocking scraping |

## Briefing Phase
| Tool | Required | When |
|------|----------|------|
| get_phase_context | YES | Start of each phase |
| voc_search | YES | Validate with VOC |
| consensus (zen) | YES | Validate TOP 3 MUPs |
| thinkdeep (zen) | RECOMMENDED | Complex decisions |

## Production Phase
| Tool | Required | When |
|------|----------|------|
| write_chapter | YES (VSL) | Each VSL chapter |
| blind_critic | YES | After any copy |
| emotional_stress_test | YES | After any copy |
| layered_review | YES | 3-layer refinement |
| black_validation | YES | Before delivery |

## Review Phase
| Tool | Required | When |
|------|----------|------|
| black_validation | YES | Final gate |
| consensus (zen) | RECOMMENDED | Multi-model validation |

## Subagent Rule
For ANY task needing MCP → use general-purpose subagent type.
Custom types (researcher, copywriter, etc) are prompt templates only.

## Model Routing
| Task | Model |
|------|-------|
| Research/VOC | sonnet |
| Briefing/Strategy | opus |
| Production (leads) | opus |
| Production (body) | sonnet |
| Validation | sonnet |
| Formatting/ETL | haiku |
